ActFinancial Consumer Agency of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment, by the Minister of Finance, of JAMES D. CALLON of Russell, Ontario, to exercise the powers and perform the duties and functions of the Commissioner of the Financial Consumer Agency of Canada for a term exceeding 90 days, until such time as a new Commissioner is appointed.
